![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/e0eb11d7-2819-4fa7-ae6b-e3a538d85412/14219.jpg?format=original)

Iyo Sky tells Rhea Ripley they can't hang out anymore because Asuka and Kairi are her family and don't want Rhea in their business.

Asuka and Kairi are creeping in the background unapprovingly. Before Rhea walks away, Iyo grabs her arm and pulls her in for a hug. Asuka gets visibly upset and storms off.

