## **_“I’m not a loser like Aston Villa or Birmingham City._**

## **_The only good thing that came outta here died a month ago. But in fairness to Ozzy Osbourne he had the good sense to move to LA. Because if I lived in Birmingham I’d die too"- Becky Lynch_**

Nikki Bella comes down to interrupt Becky Lynch and ask why she's been such a bitch.

Sunday at WWE Clash in Paris

Women’s Intercontinental Championship

Becky Lynch (c) vs. Nikki Bella

