*   ## **_Rhea Ripley def. Roxanne Perez_**
    

Post match, Raquel and Roxanne attack Rhea but Iyo Sky runs out for the save. Despite breaking up with Rhea earlier in front of Asuka who was not happy that Iyo hugged Rhea Ripley after the break up.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/ca479670-dc6a-4c25-b4b3-6aa1f718e66d/14221.jpg?format=original) ![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/68231d14-0e8a-4fc1-b2c8-f13c8484129f/14228.jpg?format=original)

Iyo Sky and Rhea Ripley are backstage. Rhea says so much for staying away from each other. Iyo says she owes Rhea for last week. Rhea says Iyo doesn't owe her anything. She walks off.

Asuka comes in screaming. She doesn't trust Rhea Ripley and now she doesn't trust Iyo. She storms off and Iyo asks Kairi to trust her but Kairi says sorry and leaves in tears

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/e618462c-5977-4a02-b030-758724166bd2/14232.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_AJ Styles def. Finn Balor_**
    

Backstage Dom finds Adam Pearce and asks him to end this AJ Styles situation for them. So Adam Pearce sets AJ Styles vs Dominik Mysterio for the IC Title next week on RAW

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/b67ff023-8be6-44ca-a01e-b2a9e99827e2/14236.jpg?format=original)

Bayley is being pulled in two directions by the light and dark sides of her personality. Lyra Valkyria has become genuinely concerned for her

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/6e82a6e1-e026-401f-be4b-d51792a46d13/14242.jpg?format=original)

Roman Reigns attacks Bronson Reed and Bron Breakker backstage. He takes out Reed while LA Knight appears and brawls Bron Breakker to the ring for the main event

* * *

*   ## **_Bron Breakker def. LA Knight_**
    

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/e11e0732-53ca-409a-bcd5-3f121722f11b/14250.jpg?format=original)

LA Knight has got Bron Breakker where he wants him but Seth Rollins gets involved with a distraction that allows Bron to hit Knight with the Super Spear.

Rollins and Breakker jump LA Knight after the match. Jey Uso runs out to save him but eats a Pedigree. CM PUNK runs out to clear the ring.

Then Punk, USO and Knight start arguing. Punk pushes LA Knight into Jey Uso. USO superkicked Knight. Stands with Punk. Then Jey Uso superkicks Punk too.